BEGIN_LICENSE_AGREEMENT

COMMENCE_LEGAL_PROCEEDINGS

SUMMON defendant
SUMMON accomplice

READ_EVIDENCE evidence.txt

DELIVER VERDICT Initial values: defendant = (defendant), accomplice = (accomplice)

DEFINE STATUTE calculate_sentence
    sentence_length = defendant * 2 + accomplice
    DELIVER VERDICT The calculated sentence length is (sentence_length) years.
END STATUTE

final_damages = defendant * accomplice * 1000
DELIVER VERDICT The final damages amount to (final_damages) dollars.

WRITE_VERDICT verdict.txt

CASE_DISMISSED

END_LICENSE_AGREEMENT